{"tid":202803,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"黃易小説討論","createTime":"2017-04-15T18:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T01:58:40.000Z","uid":69965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8dfc430293f21f016884b31e7bacdbfbb20f5d9a","tid":202803,"uid":69965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T18:35:55.000Z","msg":"個人覺得大唐雙龍傳寫得最好，人物刻畫得最深刻 師妃媗&gt;仙氣 婠婠&gt;赤足倩影<br />\n石青䃠就情節太少 ,其他嗰啲 例如尋秦記睇完都唔記得 覆雨翻雲睇到一半已經唔想睇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論，交換對角色嘅睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f32295c48dedc1330b32e70bc79f74eef814389","tid":202803,"uid":69965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T18:44:16.000Z","msg":"個人覺得女角嚟講婠婠同師妃暄刻畫得最深刻，最有血有肉，令人記得。"},{"pid":"d124155b0f080c4e503c195f325c3a48a9623a1e","tid":202803,"uid":69965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:31:06.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"1e05ea5fc696405255a961cc25ba0da1de7e427c","tid":202803,"uid":72696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T07:11:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca1bee10c4571092a404c206e8e6f0cfd48b7d7","tid":202803,"uid":155079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T00:13:22.000Z","msg":"我最鐘意尋秦記<br />\n尋秦記又有創意，又用項少龍一個角色串聯六國嘅人物<br />\n雖然每次項少龍都會無意中偷聽到人地嘅毒計，同埋掃人地對酥胸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a373c3749c4a64e19b7c0df7a3a9ca74932d5a","tid":202803,"uid":155079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T00:17:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個人覺得大唐雙龍傳寫得最好，人物刻畫得最深刻 師妃媗&gt;仙氣 婠婠&gt;赤足倩影<br />\n石青䃠就情節太少 ,其他嗰啲 例如尋秦記睇完都唔記得 覆雨翻雲睇到一半已經唔想睇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論，交換對角色嘅睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n覆雨翻雲只係得龐班同浪翻雲突出<br />\n韓柏同風行烈比較形容得無咁好，又無乜特色<br />\n<br />\n邊荒傳說一開頭幾好，講下謝玄同埋邊荒集<br />\n去到後期成個故事無啦啦痴唒線，燕飛有無線電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b83e7474655c614b7bd1321986c8a5c0d49f80","tid":202803,"uid":92083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T01:58:40.000Z","msg":"個人覺得破碎虛空幾好。因為短所以劇情進展夠順，同埋驚雁宮同護送傳鷹個兩part好正。<br />\n<br />\n雖然就官鬥打仗黎講盛唐應該係最好個部，不過角色多到連虛夜月二世都要比人放養，然後個個對手都係就破碎咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過都係好想睇埋個結局佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}